data.description: Discover the perfect blend of style and functionality in this contemporary 3-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom home spanning two stories. Situated on a corner lot in a tranquil cul-de-sac, this residence welcomes you with an open-concept design, creating a seamless flow between living spaces. The modern kitchen is adorned with sleek finishes, and the master suite provides a private retreat. With thoughtful details throughout and a prime location, this property epitomizes comfortable and convenient living.
